From 765b47d02aac894da80b74284263d1b487415aa0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Keith Winstein <208955+keithw@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Fri, 8 Nov 2024 07:45:07 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add support for the custom-page-sizes proposal (#2502)

This adds support in the binary/text parsers and writers,
the validator and interpreter, and objdump (but not wasm2c).
